# 🚀 SoyuzCode Image Generator Backend

Welcome to the **SoyuzCode Image Generator Backend**!  
This backend is designed to power a mobile app built with App Inventor, providing fast and reliable AI image enhancement using [Pollinations.ai](https://pollinations.ai/).  
Deployed on [Vercel](https://vercel.com/), it is optimized for speed and simplicity—perfect for the "Codigo TBox" competition! 🏁

---

## 🖼️ What Does It Do?

- Receives an image from the mobile app.
- Sends the image to Pollinations.ai for AI-powered enhancement.
- Returns the improved image to the app, quickly and efficiently.

---

## ⚡ Why Use This Backend?

- **Speed:** Built for rapid responses—ideal for competitive environments.
- **Simplicity:** Easy integration with App Inventor projects.
- **Reliability:** Hosted on Vercel for high availability.
- **AI Power:** Leverages Pollinations.ai for state-of-the-art image enhancement.

---

## 📲 How to Use

1. **Send a POST request** with your image to the backend endpoint.
2. **Receive the enhanced image** in the response.
3. **Display or use** the improved image in your App Inventor app!

---

## 🏆 Made for "Codigo TBox"

This backend was created as part of the "Codigo TBox" competition, focusing on delivering fast and innovative solutions.  
Feel free to use, adapt, and improve it for your own projects!

